{"tid":1850980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港龍KA853既空中服務員同乘客睇路","createTime":"2020-01-29T23:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T06:41:27.000Z","uid":87123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a66308f67cfe13674fef162fee2030733035230","tid":1850980,"uid":87123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T23:07:25.000Z","msg":"上星期仲連續幾日都係用依班機來回香港武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ab1e80c0a43fb22fc9b8b7e07afd62d888029a","tid":1850980,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/426380/武漢肺炎-武漢男乘搭國泰港龍ka853來港-轉機cx500抵日本確診\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F426380%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%94%B7%E4%B9%98%E6%90%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E6%B8%AF%E9%BE%8Dka853%E4%BE%86%E6%B8%AF-%E8%BD%89%E6%A9%9Fcx500%E6%8A%B5%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=d6dfc9c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/426380/武漢肺炎-武漢男乘搭國泰港龍ka853來港-轉機cx500抵日本確診</a><br />\n<br />\n日本昨日（23日）錄得第二宗武漢新型冠狀病毒確診個案，衞生署衞生防護中心總監黃加慶透露，接獲日本的通報，該乘客於1月19日從武漢乘坐國泰港龍KA853航班抵港，隨即轉乘國泰CX500前往日本東京，該病人抵日本後確診。本港衞生署需追查第一班航班的乘客及病人在機上的密切接觸者。"},{"pid":"36e19f6dc5fb5be1eb70c9982607056f96c44ec5","tid":1850980,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505468-20200129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505468-20200129.htm&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH0cTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=0384c063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505468-20200129.htm&h=e838d0c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505468-20200129.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增兩個新型肺炎懷疑個案，兩名病人是來自武漢的一對夫婦，分別72和73歲，上星期三乘坐KA853航班入境，昨晚送院，初步測試結果對新病毒呈陽性反應。"}]}